column5: Hi. just wondering. i have 2 camera web sites for flag island camera i think. one is a controlled cameras and the other points at a dock all the time and its called cabin camera. i was just wondering if this is from the same place or lake. thanks
Yes they are. the camera you can move is on top of a antenae tower and the other mounted by the dock. I believe they are located on the north east side of the island. Take care.
Which Lake are we talking about here?
>Which Lake are we talking about here? Lake Of The Woods, Northwest Angle
